summary: This document is an email containing flight itinerary information for a trip from Newark, NJ to St. Thomas, US Virgin Islands on January 13, 2007. It appears to be travel coordination related to Jeffrey Epstein's network, sent from an unspecified sender to an unspecified recipient.

events.title: Flight to St. Thomas
events.description: A scheduled flight from Newark Liberty International Airport (EWR) to Cyril E. King Airport (STT) in St. Thomas, US Virgin Islands, departing at 9:40 AM and arriving at 2:58 PM.

locations: St Thomas Island Cyril E King (STT)
